Package: gtksourceview-sharp
Version: 2.0
Revision: 1027
Description: C# bindings for GTKSourceView
License: LGPL
Maintainer: Benjamin Reed <gtksourceview-sharp@fink.racoonfink.com>

Depends: gtk-sharp2 (>= 2.4.2-1022), gtksourceview-shlibs (>= 1.2-1), mono (>= 1.1.16-1), mono-tools (>= 1.1.11-1022)
BuildDepends: atk1, glib2-dev (>= 2.8.6-123), gtk+2-dev, gtk-sharp2 (>= 2.4.2-1022), gtksourceview-dev (>= 1.2-1), libart2, libbonobo2-dev, libgnomeprint2.2-dev, libxml2, mono-dev (>= 1.1.14-1021), mono-tools (>= 1.1.11-1022), orbit2-dev, pango1-xft2-dev (>= 1.12.0-1001), pkgconfig

Source: http://go-mono.com/sources/%n-%v/%n-%v-0.10.tar.gz
Source-MD5: 2179634b8931e6be849a1e1f82c834e3

SetCPPFLAGS: -I%p/include
SetLIBS: -L%p/lib
SetMAKEFLAGS: -j1
NoSetCPPFLAGS: true
NoSetLDFLAGS: true
NoSetMAKEFLAGS: true
ConfigureParams: --mandir=%p/share/man --disable-dependency-tracking
CompileScript: <<
#!/bin/sh -ex

  export lt_cv_sys_max_cmd_len=65536
  perl -pi -e 's/hardcode_direct=yes/hardcode_direct=no/g' configure
  ./configure %c
  make
<<

InstallScript: <<
#!/bin/sh -ex

  export MONO_PATH="%i/lib:$MONO_PATH"
  make install DESTDIR=%d
  rm -rf %i/share/gtksourceview-1.0/language-specs
<<
DocFiles: AUTHORS COPYING* ChangeLog INSTALL NEWS README

PostInstScript:   [ -x "%p/bin/monodoc" ] && [ -d "%p/lib/monodoc" ] && "%p/bin/monodoc" --make-index >/dev/null 2>&1 || :

Homepage: http://go-mono.com/
DescDetail: <<
This package provides .NET assemblies that allow .NET / C#
programs to use the gtksourceview library.
<<

